                            Angular Features

                            1. Component [root - AppComponent]
                            2. Modules   [root - AppModule]
                            3. Data Binding
                                3.1 One way binding

                                    3.1.1 Component to view
                                        A:String Interpolation / Interpolation ({{expression}})
                                        B:Property Binding- [Binding-Target]="Binding-Source"

                                    2.1.2 View to Component
                                        A:Event binding - (event)="function call"

                                        B:Event binding using $event - (event)="function call($event)"

                                        C:Template referencing variable -(#variable name)
                                
                                 3.2 Two way binding

                                    A:NgModel -(Defined in FormsModules / syntax"[(ngModel)]="variable name"")

                            4. Dependency injection

                            5. Services

                            6. Template driven angular forms(Angular forms)

                            7. Model driven angular forms(Angular forms)

                                A: Reactive forms (ReactiveFormsModule)
                                
                                    A.1 Form Group

                                    A.2 Form Array

                                    A.3 Form Control

                            8. Angular Directives
                                A: Component Directives

                                B: Structural Directives
                                    B.1 *ngIf="condition"

                                    B.2 *ngFor

                                    B.3 *ngSwitch

                            9. Local storage (storing data in browser)

                                A setItem - To store value in local storage

                                B getItem - To retrive a valu from local storage

                                C removeItem - To remove an item from local storage

                            



 